OL,3,CUS defense secretary abruptly revokes
OL,4,Cplea deal with accused 9/11 plotters
OL,6,FThe deal reportedly would have allowed
OL,7,Fthe men to avoid the death penalty, a
OL,8,Fmove criticised by families of the
OL,9,Fvictims
OL,11,FDefense Secretary Lloyd Austin
OL,12,Fabruptly revoked a plea deal for the
OL,13,Falleged mastermind of the September
OL,14,F11, 2001, terror attacks and his co-
OL,15,Fconspirators.
OL,17,FIn a memo released on Friday, Mr
OL,18,FAustin also said he was revoking the
OL,19,Fauthority of the officer overseeing
OL,20,Fthe military court who signed the
OL,21,Fagreement on Wednesday.
