OL,3,CUS defense secretary abruptly revokes
OL,4,Cplea deal with accused 9/11 plotters
OL,6,FThe memo, addressed to Susan
OL,7,FEscallier, the convening authority for
OL,8,Fmilitary commissions who runs the
OL,9,Fmilitary courts at Guantanamo Bay,
OL,10,Fsaid the defense secretary would
OL,11,Fimmediately withdraw her authority in
OL,12,Fthe cases and "reserve such authority
OL,13,Fto (himself)."
OL,15,FMr Austin said that he was withdrawing
OL,16,Ffrom the three pre-trial agreements,
OL,17,Fwhich had taken the death penalty off
OL,18,Fthe table for the three men.
