OL,3,CUS defense secretary abruptly revokes
OL,4,Cplea deal with accused 9/11 plotters
OL,6,FOnly two days earlier, the Pentagon
OL,7,Fannounced that it had reached a plea
OL,8,Fdeal with Khalid Sheikh Mohammed, more
OL,9,Fcommonly known as KSM, and two other
OL,10,Fdefendants ` Walid Bin 'Attash, and
OL,11,FHawsawi ` accused of plotting the
OL,12,Fattacks.
OL,14,FProsecutors in the case had been
OL,15,Fdiscussing the possibility of a plea
OL,16,Fdeal for more than two years, which
OL,17,Fwould have avoided a lengthy trial
OL,18,Fcomplicated by questions over the
OL,19,Fadmissibility of evidence obtained
OL,20,Fduring torture.
