OL,3,CUS defense secretary abruptly revokes
OL,4,Cplea deal with accused 9/11 plotters
OL,6,FIn 2008, Mohammed was charged with a
OL,7,Flist of crimes including conspiracy,
OL,8,Fmurder in violation of the law of war,
OL,9,Fattacking civilians, attacking
OL,10,Fcivilian objects, intentionally
OL,11,Fcausing serious bodily injury,
OL,12,Fdestruction of property in violation
OL,13,Fof the law of war, and terrorism and
OL,14,Fmaterial support of terrorism.
OL,16,FThe US had said it would seek the
OL,17,Fdeath penalty for Mohammed.
