OL,3,CUS defense secretary abruptly revokes
OL,4,Cplea deal with accused 9/11 plotters
OL,6,FBut the military trial against
OL,7,FMohammed and his alleged co-
OL,8,Fconspirators was delayed for years as
OL,9,Fthe US tried to determine how to
OL,10,Fhandle the issue of torture used
OL,11,Fagainst Mohammed and others at secret
OL,12,FCIA prisons in the 2000s.
OL,14,FThe trial was set to begin in January
OL,15,F2021, but delays brought about by the
OL,16,Fresignation of two judges and the
OL,17,Fcoronavirus pandemic pushed the date
OL,18,Fback.
